{"tid":831793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先地鐵鬧鳩廢老","createTime":"2018-09-22T09:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T10:09:45.000Z","uid":157321,"like":62,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4414a7cfd4715f50f2042f257ea84c475b5c4d","tid":831793,"uid":157321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"話說小弟呢幾日感冒<br />\n跟住今日一早起身跑黎跑去搞d事<br />\n頭先見腳仔軟頭暈暈<br />\n搭地鐵個陣見關愛座就衝過去坐<br />\n點知坐到下個站<br />\n有個廢老上車<br />\n行我隔離拍一拍隔離無人坐既關愛座<br />\n話：「後生仔，識唔識睇字？」<br />\n跟住我即屌鳩佢：「你癡孖筋？個位老奉比你班老人家坐嫁？個個都坐得」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住佢唔再出聲<br />\n隔離d人望住都無人出聲<br />\n個下勁爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母班廢老，宜家乜柒都奉旨咁款<br />\n最撚好笑既係我隔離仲有個空既關愛座<br />\n都無阻到佢<br />\n佢都要教訓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴絲們其實以後見到呢d廢老<br />\n應該見一個屌一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一改呢個矯枉過正既歪風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b644f51f795c7a176a16f41ed6d071e2315080b4","tid":831793,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T09:34:56.000Z","msg":"好波 清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee28d5bd851dea88172d6f3f8cbc8f296f1734c","tid":831793,"uid":157321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b644f51f795c7a176a16f41ed6d071e2315080b4","tid":831793,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T09:34:56.000Z","msg":"好波 清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgm